  "prompt": "How do I apply winter internship in Rourkela Steel Plant?",
  "response": "To apply for a winter internship at the Rourkela Steel Plant (RSP), which is managed by the Steel Authority of India Limited (SAIL), you can follow these steps:\n\n### 1. **Check for Official Notifications**\n   - Visit the official website of **SAIL** ([www.sail.co.in](https://www.sail.co.in)) or the **Rourkela Steel Plant** portal.\n   - Look for notifications or announcements regarding winter internships. SAIL usually releases detailed notifications for internships, including eligibility criteria, application process, and deadlines.\n\n### 2. **Understand the Eligibility Criteria**\n   - Typically, internships are open to students pursuing engineering (e.g., Mechanical, Electrical, Civil, Metallurgy, etc.), management, or other relevant disciplines.\n   - Ensure you meet the eligibility criteria, such as academic qualifications, year of study, and percentage of marks.\n\n### 3. **Prepare Required Documents**\n   - Academic certificates and mark sheets.\n   - A valid ID proof (e.g., Aadhar card, PAN card).\n   - A letter of recommendation from your college or university (if required).\n   - A passport-sized photograph.\n\n### 4. **Submit the Application**\n   - Applications are usually submitted online through the SAIL or RSP portal.\n   - Fill out the application form with accurate details, upload the required documents, and submit it before the deadline.\n\n### 5. **Follow Up**\n   - After submitting your application, keep track of updates on the SAIL or RSP website.\n   - If shortlisted, you may be called for an interview or directly assigned an internship based on the selection process.\n\n### 6. **Contact SAIL/RSP Directly (Optional)**\n   - If you cannot find specific details about winter internships, you can contact the HR department of Rourkela Steel Plant via email or phone for clarification.\n\n### 7. **Prepare for the Internship**\n   - Once selected, prepare yourself for the internship by gathering information about the plant's operations and the specific area you\u2019ll be working in.\n\n### Important Links:\n- **SAIL Official Website**: [www.sail.co.in](https://www.sail.co.in)\n- **Rourkela Steel Plant**: Look for the RSP section on the SAIL website.\n\nMake sure to verify all details from the official sources to avoid any misinformation. Good luck with your application!",
